  Key shortcuts (i3 keybinds — D_WM stack)

  ┌──────────────────┬──────────────────────────┐
  │       Key        │          Action          │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+Enter      │ kitty                    │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+R          │ rofi launcher            │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+Tab        │ rofi window switcher     │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+E          │ thunar                   │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+Q          │ close window             │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+F          │ fullscreen               │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+1..9       │ switch workspace         │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+SHIFT+1..9 │ move window to workspace │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+h/j/k/l    │ focus window             │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+SHIFT+E    │ logout/lock/reboot menu  │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ SUPER+SHIFT+T    │ theme picker             │
  ├──────────────────┼──────────────────────────┤
  │ Print            │ flameshot screenshot     │
  └──────────────────┴──────────────────────────┘

  What's intentionally NOT shipped (add later if you want)

  - No wallpaper image — ~/.config/i3/wallpaper.sh falls back to solid color. Drop a wallpaper.png into ~/.config/i3/ and it'll show.
  - p10k not pre-configured — first interactive zsh launch will run p10k configure (about 2 min of prompts).
  - xfce4-panel keeps its default look — adding a custom panel XML or replacing with polybar is a future polish task.
  - No animated wallpapers — anime loops need xwinwrap + mpv, deferred to a future install script.

